<createdBy>Dominik</createdBy>
<createdTime>2021-07-29 12:19:55 UTC</createdTime>
<commentInRDBMS><![CDATA[A Transferable deposit is an Overnight deposit fulfilling the definition of Regulation (EU) 549/2013, 5.80:
Definition: transferable deposits are deposits exchangeable for currency on demand, at par, and which are directly usable for making payments by cheque, draft, giro order, direct debit/credit, or other direct payment facilities, without penalty or restriction.]]></commentInRDBMS>
